{"id":3602,"date":"2024-11-25T01:15:47","date_gmt":"2024-11-25T01:15:47","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/programming.team2102.org\/?page_id=3602"},"modified":"2025-01-16T05:52:05","modified_gmt":"2025-01-16T05:52:05","slug":"assembling-the-swerve-module","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"http:\/\/gabybot.com\/assembling-the-swerve-module\/","title":{"rendered":"Assembling the Swerve Modules"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<h4>Parts<\/h4>\n\n\n\n<p>The robot consists of four swerve modules. To assemble each module you will need the following 3D printed parts:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large is-resized\"><a href=\"http:\/\/programming.team2102.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/3dPartsAnotated-1.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"http:\/\/programming.team2102.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/3dPartsAnotated-1-1024x534.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-3761\" width=\"496\" height=\"258\" srcset=\"http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/3dPartsAnotated-1-1024x534.jpg 1024w, http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/3dPartsAnotated-1-300x156.jpg 300w, http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/3dPartsAnotated-1-150x78.jpg 150w, http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/3dPartsAnotated-1-768x400.jpg 768w, http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/3dPartsAnotated-1.jpg 1500w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 496px) 100vw, 496px\" \/><\/a><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>And the following set of hardware:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large is-resized\"><a href=\"http:\/\/programming.team2102.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/PartsAnotated.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"http:\/\/programming.team2102.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/PartsAnotated-1024x665.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-3751\" width=\"510\" height=\"331\" srcset=\"http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/PartsAnotated-1024x665.jpg 1024w, http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/PartsAnotated-300x195.jpg 300w, http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/PartsAnotated-150x97.jpg 150w, http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/PartsAnotated-768x499.jpg 768w, http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/PartsAnotated.jpg 1500w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 510px) 100vw, 510px\" \/><\/a><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h4>Applying the inserts<\/h4>\n\n\n\n<p>The first thing you are going to need to do is insert the various inserts into the <strong>Base<\/strong>, 60 <strong>Tooth Steering Gear,<\/strong> and <strong>Upper Support<\/strong>. In the case of the Base, the positions of the inserts depends on the corner of the robot. If you look at the Base, you will see it is marked with letters:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large is-resized\"><a href=\"http:\/\/programming.team2102.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/BaseAnotated.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"http:\/\/programming.team2102.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/BaseAnotated-1024x686.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-3763\" width=\"516\" height=\"346\" srcset=\"http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/BaseAnotated-1024x686.jpg 1024w, http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/BaseAnotated-300x201.jpg 300w, http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/BaseAnotated-150x100.jpg 150w, http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/BaseAnotated-768x514.jpg 768w, http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/BaseAnotated.jpg 1387w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 516px) 100vw, 516px\" \/><\/a><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>The holes marked with an <strong>A<\/strong> should have inserts for <strong>all <\/strong>four corners. The holes marked with <strong>BL<\/strong> should only have inserts for the <strong>back left<\/strong> corner. The holes marked <strong>!BL<\/strong> should have inserts for <strong>all <\/strong>corners <strong>except <\/strong>the <strong>back left<\/strong>. The holes marked <strong>FR<\/strong> should only have inserts for the <strong>front right<\/strong> corner. Finally the hole that is marked <strong>BR<\/strong> should only have an insert for the <strong>back right<\/strong> corner.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Also, the <strong>Upper Support<\/strong> part has a only one hole for a <strong>8-32 insert<\/strong> and that insert should only be applied for the <strong>Back Left Corner<\/strong>.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>There are two ways you can apply the inserts. The first is to use a normal soldering iron as shown below:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-full is-resized\"><a href=\"http:\/\/programming.team2102.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/InsertWithIron.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"http:\/\/programming.team2102.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/InsertWithIron.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-3660\" width=\"284\" height=\"397\" srcset=\"http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/InsertWithIron.jpg 732w, http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/InsertWithIron-214x300.jpg 214w, http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/InsertWithIron-143x200.jpg 143w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 284px) 100vw, 284px\" \/><\/a><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>Apply the iron (temperature ~250\u00b0 F) as shown. As the insert heats up you will be able to push it into the hole. Note that you do not need a lot of pressure. You should try and keep the soldering iron as vertical as possible. After the insert is all the way in, you should immediately check to see if it is in straight by screwing in a bolt and viewing it from various angles:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large is-resized\"><a href=\"http:\/\/programming.team2102.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/CheckInsert.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"http:\/\/programming.team2102.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/CheckInsert-1024x640.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-3662\" width=\"425\" height=\"265\" srcset=\"http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/CheckInsert-1024x640.jpg 1024w, http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/CheckInsert-300x187.jpg 300w, http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/CheckInsert-150x94.jpg 150w, http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/CheckInsert-768x480.jpg 768w, http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/CheckInsert-1536x960.jpg 1536w, http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/CheckInsert.jpg 1636w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 425px) 100vw, 425px\" \/><\/a><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>If you do this right after you apply the insert, the plastic will be soft enough that you can reposition it if necessary. Note that if you later find that one of your screws is not straight, you can fix it by using a soldering iron to reheat the insert until the plastic is soft enough to reposition it.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>The second way to apply the inserts is to use a tool such as <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https:\/\/www.amazon.com\/dp\/B0D22MLFMD?ref=ppx_yo2ov_dt_b_fed_asin_title\" target=\"_blank\">this one<\/a>. While this tool helps get the inserts straight, it is by no means foolproof and you should still check to make sure that they are straight.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>If you really don&#8217;t want to be bothered by the inserts, you can, if you wish, use longer bolts and have them go through the holes and attach with a nut on the other side. However, despite the fact that applying them is a bit of a pain, you will find that it well worthwhile as it make assembling the robot much easier.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Once you have applied the inserts and let them all cool, you need to check the other side for plastic that has been pushed into a position that partially blocks the screw:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-full is-resized\"><a href=\"http:\/\/programming.team2102.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/CleanInsertHole.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"http:\/\/programming.team2102.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/CleanInsertHole.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-3671\" width=\"414\" height=\"310\" srcset=\"http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/CleanInsertHole.jpg 1024w, http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/CleanInsertHole-300x225.jpg 300w, http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/CleanInsertHole-150x113.jpg 150w, http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/CleanInsertHole-768x576.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 414px) 100vw, 414px\" \/><\/a><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>You should use a exacto knife to clean out the blocking plastic and then run a bolt all the way through to make sure it is clear.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-full is-resized\"><a href=\"http:\/\/programming.team2102.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/ClearInsert.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"http:\/\/programming.team2102.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/ClearInsert.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-3672\" width=\"415\" height=\"283\" srcset=\"http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/ClearInsert.jpg 1024w, http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/ClearInsert-300x205.jpg 300w, http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/ClearInsert-150x103.jpg 150w, http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/ClearInsert-768x525.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 415px) 100vw, 415px\" \/><\/a><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>The following shows the 3 parts that require inserts after the inserts have been applied. Note that these insert positions are for the <strong>Back Left Corner<\/strong>.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-full is-resized\"><a href=\"http:\/\/programming.team2102.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/PartsWithInserts.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"http:\/\/programming.team2102.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/PartsWithInserts.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-3675\" width=\"449\" height=\"389\" srcset=\"http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/PartsWithInserts.jpg 1024w, http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/PartsWithInserts-300x261.jpg 300w, http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/PartsWithInserts-150x130.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 449px) 100vw, 449px\" \/><\/a><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h4>Assemble the wheel<\/h4>\n\n\n\n<p>Insert a <strong>10x15x4 Bearing<\/strong> into each side of the wheel as shown:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large is-resized\"><a href=\"http:\/\/programming.team2102.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/WheelBearing.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"http:\/\/programming.team2102.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/WheelBearing-1024x499.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-3720\" width=\"572\" height=\"279\" srcset=\"http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/WheelBearing-1024x499.jpg 1024w, http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/WheelBearing-300x146.jpg 300w, http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/WheelBearing-150x73.jpg 150w, http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/WheelBearing-768x374.jpg 768w, http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/WheelBearing-1536x749.jpg 1536w, http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/WheelBearing-2048x998.jpg 2048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 572px) 100vw, 572px\" \/><\/a><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>Now insert the two <strong>Wheel Spacers<\/strong> into the wheel bearings as shown:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large is-resized\"><a href=\"http:\/\/programming.team2102.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/WheelBearingWithSpacer.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"http:\/\/programming.team2102.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/WheelBearingWithSpacer-1024x522.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-3723\" width=\"563\" height=\"287\" srcset=\"http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/WheelBearingWithSpacer-1024x522.jpg 1024w, http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/WheelBearingWithSpacer-300x153.jpg 300w, http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/WheelBearingWithSpacer-150x76.jpg 150w, http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/WheelBearingWithSpacer-768x391.jpg 768w, http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/WheelBearingWithSpacer-1536x783.jpg 1536w, http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/WheelBearingWithSpacer.jpg 2010w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 563px) 100vw, 563px\" \/><\/a><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>Then place the rubber <strong>Wrist Band<\/strong> around the wheel for traction as shown:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-full is-resized\"><a href=\"http:\/\/programming.team2102.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/WheelWithBand.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"http:\/\/programming.team2102.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/WheelWithBand.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-3726\" width=\"244\" height=\"215\" srcset=\"http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/WheelWithBand.jpg 1024w, http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/WheelWithBand-300x265.jpg 300w, http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/WheelWithBand-150x133.jpg 150w, http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/WheelWithBand-768x679.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 244px) 100vw, 244px\" \/><\/a><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h4>Assemble the Base<\/h4>\n\n\n\n<p>First insert the  <strong>60x78x10 Bearing<\/strong> into the <strong>Base <\/strong>as shown:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-full is-resized\"><a href=\"http:\/\/programming.team2102.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/BaseWithBearing.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"http:\/\/programming.team2102.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/BaseWithBearing.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-3681\" width=\"337\" height=\"193\" srcset=\"http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/BaseWithBearing.jpg 1024w, http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/BaseWithBearing-300x172.jpg 300w, http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/BaseWithBearing-150x86.jpg 150w, http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/BaseWithBearing-768x441.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 337px) 100vw, 337px\" \/><\/a><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>Next insert the <strong>Pot Coupler<\/strong> into the <strong>Base With Arms<\/strong> as shown:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-full is-resized\"><a href=\"http:\/\/programming.team2102.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/BaseWithArmsPlusPotCoupler.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"http:\/\/programming.team2102.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/BaseWithArmsPlusPotCoupler.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-3684\" width=\"196\" height=\"237\" srcset=\"http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/BaseWithArmsPlusPotCoupler.jpg 843w, http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/BaseWithArmsPlusPotCoupler-247x300.jpg 247w, http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/BaseWithArmsPlusPotCoupler-150x182.jpg 150w, http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/BaseWithArmsPlusPotCoupler-768x933.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 196px) 100vw, 196px\" \/><\/a><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>Then insert the <strong>12x18x4 Bearing<\/strong> into the <strong>60 Tooth Steering Gear<\/strong> as shown:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-full is-resized\"><a href=\"http:\/\/programming.team2102.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/60ToothSteeringGearPlusBearing.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"http:\/\/programming.team2102.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/60ToothSteeringGearPlusBearing.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-3687\" width=\"227\" height=\"218\" srcset=\"http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/60ToothSteeringGearPlusBearing.jpg 1024w, http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/60ToothSteeringGearPlusBearing-300x289.jpg 300w, http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/60ToothSteeringGearPlusBearing-150x144.jpg 150w, http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/60ToothSteeringGearPlusBearing-768x740.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 227px) 100vw, 227px\" \/><\/a><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>Next insert one of the <strong>10x15x4 Bearings<\/strong> into the <strong>Base With Arms<\/strong> as shown:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-full is-resized\"><a href=\"http:\/\/programming.team2102.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/BaseWithArmsPlusBearing.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"http:\/\/programming.team2102.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/BaseWithArmsPlusBearing.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-3690\" width=\"167\" height=\"240\" srcset=\"http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/BaseWithArmsPlusBearing.jpg 712w, http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/BaseWithArmsPlusBearing-209x300.jpg 209w, http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/BaseWithArmsPlusBearing-139x200.jpg 139w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 167px) 100vw, 167px\" \/><\/a><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>Then insert the <strong>Lower Bevel Bearing<\/strong> into the <strong>10x15x4<\/strong> Bearing that you just inserted into the Base With Arms as shown:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-full is-resized\"><a href=\"http:\/\/programming.team2102.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/LowerBevelBearingInsertedAnotated.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"http:\/\/programming.team2102.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/LowerBevelBearingInsertedAnotated.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-3693\" width=\"158\" height=\"223\" srcset=\"http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/LowerBevelBearingInsertedAnotated.jpg 726w, http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/LowerBevelBearingInsertedAnotated-213x300.jpg 213w, http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/LowerBevelBearingInsertedAnotated-142x200.jpg 142w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 158px) 100vw, 158px\" \/><\/a><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>Now insert the <strong>Square Shaft<\/strong> through the <strong>Bevel Pinion<\/strong> and into the <strong>Lower Bevel Bearing<\/strong> as shown:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-full is-resized\"><a href=\"http:\/\/programming.team2102.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/BevelBearingPlusSquareShaft.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"http:\/\/programming.team2102.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/BevelBearingPlusSquareShaft.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-3694\" width=\"244\" height=\"175\" srcset=\"http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/BevelBearingPlusSquareShaft.jpg 1024w, http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/BevelBearingPlusSquareShaft-300x216.jpg 300w, http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/BevelBearingPlusSquareShaft-150x108.jpg 150w, http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/BevelBearingPlusSquareShaft-768x553.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 244px) 100vw, 244px\" \/><\/a><figcaption><br><\/figcaption><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>Next attach the <strong>12 Tooth Drive Gear<\/strong> to the <strong>Square Shaft<\/strong> as shown:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-full is-resized\"><a href=\"http:\/\/programming.team2102.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/12TDriveGearAttached.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"http:\/\/programming.team2102.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/12TDriveGearAttached.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-3697\" width=\"212\" height=\"215\" srcset=\"http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/12TDriveGearAttached.jpg 1007w, http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/12TDriveGearAttached-295x300.jpg 295w, http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/12TDriveGearAttached-150x153.jpg 150w, http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/12TDriveGearAttached-768x781.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 212px) 100vw, 212px\" \/><\/a><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>Then insert the <strong>Base With Arms<\/strong> into the <strong>Base <\/strong>as shown:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-full is-resized\"><a href=\"http:\/\/programming.team2102.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/BaseWithArmsInBase.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"http:\/\/programming.team2102.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/BaseWithArmsInBase.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-3699\" width=\"262\" height=\"278\" srcset=\"http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/BaseWithArmsInBase.jpg 962w, http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/BaseWithArmsInBase-282x300.jpg 282w, http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/BaseWithArmsInBase-150x160.jpg 150w, http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/BaseWithArmsInBase-768x817.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 262px) 100vw, 262px\" \/><\/a><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>Now attach the <strong>60 Tooth Steering Gear<\/strong> to the <strong>Base With Arms<\/strong> with two <strong>7\/8&#8243; 4-40 Screws<\/strong> as shown:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large is-resized\"><a href=\"http:\/\/programming.team2102.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/60ToothSterringAttachedBothSides.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"http:\/\/programming.team2102.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/60ToothSterringAttachedBothSides-1024x504.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-3732\" width=\"532\" height=\"262\" srcset=\"http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/60ToothSterringAttachedBothSides-1024x504.jpg 1024w, http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/60ToothSterringAttachedBothSides-300x148.jpg 300w, http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/60ToothSterringAttachedBothSides-150x74.jpg 150w, http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/60ToothSterringAttachedBothSides-768x378.jpg 768w, http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/60ToothSterringAttachedBothSides-1536x756.jpg 1536w, http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/60ToothSterringAttachedBothSides-2048x1008.jpg 2048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 532px) 100vw, 532px\" \/><\/a><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>Then place two <strong>10x15x4 Bearings<\/strong> on the <strong>Pot Coupler<\/strong> and lock them in place with the <strong>Inner Race Spacer<\/strong> as shown:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large is-resized\"><a href=\"http:\/\/programming.team2102.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/BearingsOnPotCouplerAnotated.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"http:\/\/programming.team2102.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/BearingsOnPotCouplerAnotated-961x1024.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-3711\" width=\"337\" height=\"358\" srcset=\"http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/BearingsOnPotCouplerAnotated-961x1024.jpg 961w, http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/BearingsOnPotCouplerAnotated-282x300.jpg 282w, http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/BearingsOnPotCouplerAnotated-150x160.jpg 150w, http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/BearingsOnPotCouplerAnotated-768x818.jpg 768w, http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/BearingsOnPotCouplerAnotated.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 337px) 100vw, 337px\" \/><\/a><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>Now slide the <strong>Center Drive Gear<\/strong> over the two bearings that you just installed as shown:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large is-resized\"><a href=\"http:\/\/programming.team2102.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/CenterDriveGearInstalled.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"http:\/\/programming.team2102.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/CenterDriveGearInstalled-1003x1024.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-3714\" width=\"350\" height=\"357\" srcset=\"http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/CenterDriveGearInstalled-1003x1024.jpg 1003w, http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/CenterDriveGearInstalled-294x300.jpg 294w, http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/CenterDriveGearInstalled-150x153.jpg 150w, http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/CenterDriveGearInstalled-768x784.jpg 768w, http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/CenterDriveGearInstalled-1505x1536.jpg 1505w, http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/CenterDriveGearInstalled.jpg 1744w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 350px) 100vw, 350px\" \/><\/a><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>Next, attach the <strong>Wheel <\/strong>to the <strong>Base With Arms<\/strong> with the <strong>2&#8243; 8-32 Screw<\/strong> as shown:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-full is-resized\"><a href=\"http:\/\/programming.team2102.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/WheelAttached.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"http:\/\/programming.team2102.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/WheelAttached.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-3729\" width=\"337\" height=\"311\" srcset=\"http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/WheelAttached.jpg 1024w, http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/WheelAttached-300x277.jpg 300w, http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/WheelAttached-150x139.jpg 150w, http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/WheelAttached-768x710.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 337px) 100vw, 337px\" \/><\/a><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>Now mount the <strong>Steering Motor<\/strong> (the motor that does not have an encoder) to the <strong>Base<\/strong> as shown:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-full is-resized\"><a href=\"http:\/\/programming.team2102.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/SteeringMotorMounted.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"http:\/\/programming.team2102.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/SteeringMotorMounted.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-3735\" width=\"387\" height=\"230\" srcset=\"http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/SteeringMotorMounted.jpg 1024w, http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/SteeringMotorMounted-300x178.jpg 300w, http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/SteeringMotorMounted-150x89.jpg 150w, http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/SteeringMotorMounted-768x456.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 387px) 100vw, 387px\" \/><\/a><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>Finally, attach the<strong> Steering Gear<\/strong> to the <strong>Steering Motor<\/strong> using the washer and 2.5m Screws as shown:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-full is-resized\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"http:\/\/programming.team2102.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/SteeringGearInstalled.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-4104\" width=\"356\" height=\"288\" srcset=\"http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/SteeringGearInstalled.jpg 1024w, http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/SteeringGearInstalled-300x243.jpg 300w, http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/SteeringGearInstalled-150x122.jpg 150w, http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/01\/SteeringGearInstalled-768x623.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 356px) 100vw, 356px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>Before you move on, you should apply a generous amount of your favorite gear lubricant to the gears. I have been using generic petroleum jelly for my lubricant and it seems to work well. Your milage might vary.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h4>Assemble Upper Support<\/h4>\n\n\n\n<p>First attach the <strong>Drive Motor<\/strong> (the motor with the encoder) to the <strong>Upper Support<\/strong> and attack the <strong>Drive Gear<\/strong> with the <strong>Washer <\/strong>and a <strong>2.5m Screw<\/strong> as shown. Once again apply a liberal amount of gear lubricant to the gear.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large is-resized\"><a href=\"http:\/\/programming.team2102.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/UpperMotorAssembly.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"http:\/\/programming.team2102.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/UpperMotorAssembly-1024x446.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-3742\" width=\"621\" height=\"270\" srcset=\"http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/UpperMotorAssembly-1024x446.jpg 1024w, http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/UpperMotorAssembly-300x131.jpg 300w, http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/UpperMotorAssembly-150x65.jpg 150w, http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/UpperMotorAssembly-768x334.jpg 768w, http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/UpperMotorAssembly-1536x669.jpg 1536w, http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/UpperMotorAssembly-2048x892.jpg 2048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 621px) 100vw, 621px\" \/><\/a><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>Next attach the <strong>Upper Support<\/strong> to the <strong>Base <\/strong>using the four <strong>Upper Support Spacers<\/strong> and four <strong>1.5&#8243; 8-32 Screws<\/strong> as shown:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-full is-resized\"><a href=\"http:\/\/programming.team2102.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/UpperSupportAssembly.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"http:\/\/programming.team2102.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/UpperSupportAssembly.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-3745\" width=\"423\" height=\"254\" srcset=\"http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/UpperSupportAssembly.jpg 1024w, http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/UpperSupportAssembly-300x180.jpg 300w, http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/UpperSupportAssembly-150x90.jpg 150w, http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/UpperSupportAssembly-768x462.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 423px) 100vw, 423px\" \/><\/a><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>Then attach the <strong>Motor Controller Mount<\/strong> to the <strong>Base <\/strong>using two <strong>1\/2&#8243; 8-32 Screws<\/strong> and attach the Motor Controller to the <strong>Mount <\/strong>using four <strong>2-28 Screws<\/strong> as shown:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-full is-resized\"><a href=\"http:\/\/programming.team2102.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/MotorController.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"http:\/\/programming.team2102.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/MotorController.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-3770\" width=\"230\" height=\"216\" srcset=\"http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/MotorController.jpg 1024w, http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/MotorController-300x282.jpg 300w, http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/MotorController-150x141.jpg 150w, http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/MotorController-768x722.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 230px) 100vw, 230px\" \/><\/a><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>Now attach the <strong>Absolute Encoder<\/strong> to the <strong>Upper Support<\/strong> using two <strong>3\/8&#8243; 2-28 Screws <\/strong>as shown:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-full is-resized\"><a href=\"http:\/\/programming.team2102.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/Encoder.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"http:\/\/programming.team2102.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/Encoder.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-3772\" width=\"244\" height=\"239\" srcset=\"http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/Encoder.jpg 1024w, http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/Encoder-300x295.jpg 300w, http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/Encoder-150x147.jpg 150w, http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/Encoder-768x755.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 244px) 100vw, 244px\" \/><\/a><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>The <strong>Swerve Module<\/strong> is now complete. You will need to assemble four of these.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"http:\/\/programming.team2102.org\/wiring-harnesses\/\" data-type=\"page\" data-id=\"3835\">Next: Wiring Cables<\/a><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Parts The robot consists of four swerve modules. To assemble each module you will need the following 3D printed parts: And the following set of hardware: Applying the inserts The first thing you are going to need to do is insert the various inserts into the Base, 60 Tooth Steering Gear, and Upper Support. In&hellip;&nbsp;<a href=\"http:\/\/gabybot.com\/assembling-the-swerve-module\/\" class=\"\" rel=\"bookmark\">Read More &raquo;<span class=\"screen-reader-text\">Assembling the Swerve Modules<\/span><\/a><\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":2,"featured_media":0,"parent":0,"menu_order":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"open","template":"","meta":{"neve_meta_sidebar":"","neve_meta_container":"","neve_meta_enable_content_width":"","neve_meta_content_width":0,"neve_meta_title_alignment":"","neve_meta_author_avatar":"","neve_post_elements_order":"","neve_meta_disable_header":"","neve_meta_disable_footer":"","neve_meta_disable_title":""},"_links":{"self":[{"href":"http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/3602"}],"collection":[{"href":"http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages"}],"about":[{"href":"http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/page"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/2"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=3602"}],"version-history":[{"count":54,"href":"http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/3602\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":4106,"href":"http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/3602\/revisions\/4106"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"http:\/\/gabybot.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=3602"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templa